	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/07/31/morning-agenda-bank-of-america-and-u-s-far-apart-on-deal/" data-title="Morning Agenda: Bank of America and U.S. Far Apart on Deal" data-description="Bank of America and the Justice Department are still far apart on a mortgage settlement. | Argentina has found a relentless foe in Paul E. Singer. | G.E.&#039;s Synchrony Financial begins trading on Thursday. | BNP Paribas posts a record quarterly loss.">
